io.github.kensuke1984.kibrary.dsminformation

クラス PolynomialStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.kensuke1984.kibrary.dsminformation.PolynomialStructure
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PolynomialStructure
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    (input) Structure of the Earth for softwares of Direct Solution Method (DSM)

    Every depth is written in radius.

    This class is IMMUTABLE

    When you try to get values on radius of boundaries, you will get one in the isShallower layer, i.e., the layer which has the radius as rmin.

    関連項目:
    直列化された形式

      • addBoundaries

        public PolynomialStructure addBoundaries(double... radii)
        半径boundariesのところに境界を作る（層を一つ増やす） Add boundaries at the input radii. if there is already a boundary at r then nothing will be done.
        パラメータ:
        radii - radii for boundaries. Values smaller than 0 or bigger than earth radius will be ignored
        戻り値:
        a new structure which have additional layers at the input boundaries or this if there all the radiuses already exist in this
